data.description: This 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2-story home is well distributed with vaulted ceilings, large windows and bright ceramic floors offering a clean fresh feel with plenty of natural light. Upon entry, through two large double doors the first floor features a foyer, two family living rooms, dinning room, kitchen, bathroom, spare bedroom and laundry room. Through a main L-shaped stair case, enter the second floor hosting 3 main bedrooms, which all have large windows and recess-ceiling lights, as well as double-door closets and crown molding. Enjoy the extra large main bedroom, which includes a den for office or recreational use, as well as large his and hers walk-in closet, and a large master bathroom with his and hers sinks, bathtub and shower. Call me to come see your next home!
